<stack-static>
    <statement><p><p>
Determine whether the following number is even or odd.
<me>
{10}^2 + {21}
</me>
</p>

<p>
[ Even | Odd ]  
</p></p></statement>
    <solution><p><h3>Worked Solution</h3>

<p>
First evaluate the square:
</p>

<p>
<me>
{10}^2 = {100}
</me>
</p>

<p>
Now add <m>{21}</m>:
</p>

<p>
<me>
{100} + {21} = {121}
</me>
</p>

<p>
Since <m>{121}</m> is not divisible by 2,
the number is <alert>Odd</alert>.
</p></p></solution>
    <answer><p>Odd</p></answer>
</stack-static>